{
  "events": {
    "default": {
      "title": "路边奇遇",
      "steps": {
        "start": {
          "text": "道路在雾气里延伸，一段短暂的插曲等待你做出选择。",
          "options": [
            {
              "label": "搜寻",
              "description": "获得1-3金币",
              "actions": [
                { "type": "grantRandomGold", "min": 1, "max": 3 },
                { "type": "finish" }
              ]
            },
            {
              "label": "离开",
              "description": "什么也不做，继续前进",
              "actions": [{ "type": "finish" }]
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    "2": {
      "steps": {
        "start": {
          "title": "Rest Site",
          "text": "The party takes a brief rest before moving on.",
          "options": [
            {
              "label": "Continue",
              "description": "Return to the map",
              "actions": [{ "type": "finish" }]
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    "100": {
      "title": "林间祭坛",
      "steps": {
        "start": {
          "text": "你在林间发现一座发光的古老祭坛，石面上的符文像呼吸一样明灭。",
          "options": [
            {
              "label": "献上金币",
              "description": "失去10金币，获得一张随机卡牌",
              "requiresGold": 10,
              "actions": [
                { "type": "loseGold", "amount": 10 },
                { "type": "grantRandomCard" },
                { "type": "finish" }
              ]
            },
            {
              "label": "触摸符文",
              "description": "进入一场战斗，胜利后继续调查",
              "actions": [
                {
                  "type": "startBattle",
                  "returnStepId": "afterBattle",
                  "battle": { "kind": "normal" }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "label": "汲取微光",
              "description": "恢复8点生命，不超过生命上限",
              "actions": [
                { "type": "heal", "amount": 8 },
                { "type": "finish" }
              ]
            },
            {
              "label": "磨炼卡牌",
              "description": "选择一张未到三星的卡，升一星",
              "requirements": [{ "type": "hasTrainableCard" }],
              "actions": [
                {
                  "type": "chooseOwnedCard",
                  "prompt": "选择一张未到三星的卡，升一星",
                  "filter": "starBelow3",
                  "onChoose": [
                    { "type": "upgradeSelectedOwnedCard" },
                    { "type": "finish" }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        "afterBattle": {
          "text": "守护祭坛的敌人消散了，符文余光凝成一小簇温热的碎片。",
          "options": [
            {
              "label": "收下碎片",
              "description": "获得3-6金币",
              "actions": [
                { "type": "grantRandomGold", "min": 3, "max": 6 },
                { "type": "finish" }
              ]
            },
            {
              "label": "修整片刻",
              "description": "恢复5点生命",
              "actions": [
                { "type": "heal", "amount": 5 },
                { "type": "finish" }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    "400": {
      "title": "彩票店",
      "backgroundPath": "assets/events/lottery_shop.png",
      "steps": {
        "start": {
          "text": "你路过一家彩票店，就像看到野生的宝箱？难道你不想看看究竟是宝箱还是宝箱怪？",
          "options": [
            {
              "label": "试试3元的",
              "description": "小赌怡情，大赌伤身",
              "requiresGold": 3,
              "actions": [
                {
                  "type": "lotteryScratch",
                  "amount": 3,
                  "payouts": [
                    { "value": 0, "weight": 3 },
                    { "value": 1, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 2, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 3, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 4, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 5, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 6, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 7, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 8, "weight": 1 }
                  ],
                  "winText": "\"小赌怡情，大赌伤身\"，你默念着，却已经想要下一张了。",
                  "loseText": "你笑着把它丢进垃圾桶，心里骂了一句\"果然\"。",
                  "evenText": "\"保本了\"，你觉得这是今天最大的安慰。",
                  "resultSuffix": "无论如何，你还要继续赶路了。"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "label": "试试5元的",
              "description": "你感觉今天幸运女神站在你这边",
              "requiresGold": 5,
              "actions": [
                {
                  "type": "lotteryScratch",
                  "amount": 5,
                  "payouts": [
                    { "value": 0, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 1, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 2, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 3, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 4, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 5, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 6, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 7, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 8, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 9, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 10, "weight": 1 }
                  ],
                  "winText": "五块刮出{payout}块，你差点亲一口那张彩票。",
                  "loseText": "\"今天运气女神站在我这边\"。你刮出个{payout}，女神下班了。",
                  "evenText": "五块变五块，你叹了口气，\"白激动一场\"。",
                  "resultSuffix": "无论如何，你还要继续赶路了。"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "label": "试试10元的",
              "description": "上面写着超级大奖40元，万一呢？",
              "requiresGold": 10,
              "actions": [
                {
                  "type": "lotteryScratch",
                  "amount": 10,
                  "payouts": [
                    { "value": 5, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 6, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 7, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 8, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 9, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 10, "weight": 1 },
                    { "value": 40, "weight": 4 }
                  ],
                  "winText": "十块刮出四十块，你面不改色揣进兜里，出门差点撞门上。",
                  "loseText": "十块刮了个寂寞，你站在门口吹了会儿风，决定戒赌到明天早上。",
                  "evenText": "十块变十块，你反复看了三遍，最后说：“行吧，没亏就是赢。”",
                  "resultSuffix": "无论如何，你还要继续赶路了。"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "label": "直接离开",
              "description": "真的不试一试吗？",
              "actions": [
                {
                  "type": "goToStep",
                  "stepId": "leave"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        "leave": {
          "text": "你转过身去。省下这笔钱。概率从来不站在任何人一边，这是设计好的游戏。\n可你还是回头看了一眼。橱窗里的刮刮乐亮晶晶的，像一个个未完待续的故事。\n你笑了笑，推门走了出去。\n\n无论如何，你还要继续赶路了。",
          "options": [
            {
              "label": "离开",
              "description": "继续赶路",
              "actions": [{ "type": "finish" }]
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
